{
 "name": "RPlog_Meeting_with_Petra_and_Davyd",
 "title": "A Meeting with Petra and Davyd",
 "summary": "On a moonlit, deserted beach in Coronet City under an Imperial lockdown, the smuggler Axel meets the cold, statuesque Petra and her watchful bodyguard Davyd to negotiate a contract. Over old flirtation and grim business, Petra makes clear she wants certain Imperial traitors -- chief among them her former ambassador Dareus -- dead, and is willing to name any price. Axel, apathetic and mercenary, agrees to see what he can do, though he warns that he owes a favor to one of the targets, Kiare Quinn. As a token of the deal, Petra has Davyd hand over a valuable ST-III blaster rifle, and the parties seal their dark arrangement.",
